Former Big Brother Naija’s housemate, Khafi, has announced that her first-ever short film will premier today by 7 pm. Khafi said this in a tweet earlier today.

She said:

“Hi my name is Khafi and amongst many things, I am an actress. My first short film will be premiering by 7pm • I really hope you enjoy it”.

According to Khafi, the movie will be streamed online via her YouTube channel, http://YouTube.com/khafikareem.

Khafi Kareem (born 1990) of bbnaija 2019 housemate is a full-time police officer with the Metropolitan Police, UK. She hails from Ekiti State but resides in London, Uk